I think you seriosuly under estimate how many people are in this "1 % population" it's not 1% and i wish people would stop using that as a scapegoat. When EQ released that information, they went by all charachters created, including lvl 1 bazaar traders etc... You know how many people in that "1%" have 7 other charachters on their account that aren't in that "1%"? you can have one charachter in that "1%" but with the other 7 you have on your account, you're now only showing 11% even though you're in that 1%.
