<br />

<br />
If you do the math and figure out with max focus, max aa's, etc...not accounting for crits (it's too variable for both wizards and mages, but wizards will do it more), not taking into account any resists (again, too variable and no way to calculate), you'll see that even when adding our pet's dps in addition to our nuke, we far underperform wizards in dps.  Figure in the bit of extra that we do based on damage shield and it will probably bring the gap closer.  I don't quite see how you figure that you out-damage a similarly equipped wizard from your guild.
