</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">4) I have not seen Thott's post on the subject. Do you have a link by any chance? But in talking to him, I believe his impression was that wizards consistently underperfom mages so I am curious why that differs from what you read. 
