He'll remember the post for sure, and likely has a copy of it, as detailed as he is.  I can't supply a link that's usable.  However, as a Mage with max AA's in everything, and one who doesn't use Sini or Sinia as a rule in LDoN, I can tell you I'm pretty surprised to hear you say you're outdamaging Wizards.  But then, I don't have my own parses to back that statement up.
<br />

<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">5) The majority of Thott's groups have been LDON normal, which I imagine were finished in under 20 minutes. This would also skew the picture on wizard damage. 
<br />
